---
// src/components/Contact.astro
---
<section id="contact" class="py-40 bg-white text-black text-center relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-black/5"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.5em] text-[#FF5F00] uppercase font-black mb-10 block italic font-['Inter']">
      Boutique Partnership Model
    </span>
    
    <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-[900] uppercase italic tracking-tighter mb-12 leading-[0.85] font-['Inter'] text-black">
      High-Touch Focus.<br/>
      <span class="text-transparent" style="-webkit-text-stroke: 1px #000;">Unrivaled Results.</span>
    </h2>
    
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8 mb-20">
        <p class="text-black/70 uppercase text-[11px] md:text-sm tracking-[0.1em] leading-relaxed font-medium font-['Inter']">
            We operate as an extension of your board, not just another vendor. To maintain our standard of strategic obsession and creative excellence, we operate through a strictly <span class="text-black font-bold italic underline decoration-[#FF5F00] decoration-2">curated partnership model.</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-black/30 uppercase text-[9px] tracking-[0.2em] italic font-['Inter']">
            Nós operamos como uma extensão da sua diretoria. Para garantir nosso padrão de obsessão estratégica e excelência criativa, operamos através de um modelo de parceria estritamente curado.
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8">
        <a 
          href="https://wa.me/55XXXXXXXXXXX" 
          target="_blank"
          class="group relative inline-block bg-black text-white font-[900] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] px-20 py-8 text-xs hover:bg-[#FF5F00] transition-all duration-700 font-['Inter'] shadow-2xl hover:shadow-[#FF5F00]/20"
        >
          <span class="relative z-10">Apply for a Partnership</span>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FF5F00] scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform origin-left duration-500"></div>
        </a>
        
        <span class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold opacity-20 font-['Inter'] animate-pulse">
            Currently vetting brand partners for Q2 2026
        </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>